# Drop Apple Health cadence screenshots here as visual reference for the
# handoff doc one level up. AirDrop from phone → Mac → drag in.
#
# Suggested filenames:
#   01-cadence-picker.png            -- the five-option list
#   02-every-day.png                 -- (optional, the cadence picker shows this)
#   03-cyclical-day-unit.png         -- "Use for 21 days / Pause for 7 days"
#   04-cyclical-week-unit.png        -- "Use for 3 weeks / Pause for 1 week"
#   05-specific-days-single.png      -- one schedule group
#   06-specific-days-two-groups.png  -- the "Schedule Other Days" example
#   07-every-few-days.png            -- the "Every Other Day" mode
#   08-every-few-days-interval.png   -- the interval picker dropdown
#
# Not a hard requirement; the README.md doc has text annotations that
# stand on their own.
